(ooc)<br>
Vah Shir Shaman, probably all Vah Shir, have no choice other than Agnostic at character creation time. I think that this was one of the many unfinished bits at the SoL release. Don't the Kerrans on Norrath follow Prexus?<br>
<br>
We also seem to be viewed as a &quot;good&quot; race by Norrathians. Even being agnostic, we are KOS at the Overthere outpost, unlike agnostic members of the &quot;neutral&quot; Human and Gnome races, who are tolerated there.<br>
(/ooc)<br>
